defaultQ5 default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultMrs defaultGlindondefault:default 
defaultIs the 
defaultpurpose of revenue support to ensure that everybody would receive the same level of 
defaultlocal 
defaultservice if they were paying a notional uniform council tax across the board?
defaultBrandon Lewisdefault: The idea of every single person in the country paying the same council tax would be an interesting thing to take forward, and some councils might have different views on that to others.  The money 
defaultthat is distributed through grant predominantly—and obviously the most deprived areas get the highest amount of grant—is in order to make sure they can provide 
defaultthe core services.  Depending on where you are, different councils will make decisions on what their primary focus is and what their priorities are.  I have said to this Committee before everybody expects to have their waste collected—the Secretary of State would argue vehemently that it should be on a weekly basis—and to have the streets kept clean, but the priorities for an individual authority are a matter for the local authority.  That is localism.
default&#xa0;
defaultQ6 default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultMrs defaultGlindondefault:default So there would be different problems in urban and, perhaps, rural areas.
defaultBrandon Lewisdefault: I am sure some local authorities would argue that there are not only different issues to deal with in a rural area compared to an urban area, which is undoubtedly true.  In an urban area you are dealing with density of population but in close proximity to each other, generally, because of how it is built up; a more rural area will be dealing with higher transport costs or gaps and differences between areas and villages.  Equally, you will find rural areas will make the point, depending on where they are and their proximity to the next town, that they are dealing with different issues according to their area—and the same with urban areas.  I have two of the most deprived wards in the country in my constituency.  Great 
defaultYarmouth
